NK015(ba)006:0: rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba
NK015(ba)006:1: ji ltar brgyud pa'i srol 'dzin gyi dge ba'i bshes
NK015(ba)006:2: gnyen chen po rnams la gsol ba 'debs pa'i tshigs
NK015(ba)006:3: su bcad pa skal ldan thar bar 'gro ba'i sa
NK015(ba)006:4: mkhan zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)006:5: dag chen gdod ma'i dbyings su rang rig pa'i //
NK015(ba)006:6: ye shes mngon byang chub pa kun bzang zhal //
NK015(ba)006:7: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i phyag rgyar yongs shar ba //
NK015(ba)006:8: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs lnga'i gtso la 'dud //
NK015(ba)006:9: khyab bdag rgyal ba gang de'i ye shes kyi //
NK015(ba)006:10: rnam grangs sems dpa' dang ni 'joms pa yi //
NK015(ba)006:11: khyad par cir yang snang bar mdzad pa las //
NK015(ba)006:12: mchog gyur nye sras brgyad la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK015(ba)006:13: de lta'i rgyal dang de sras dgongs pa'i klong //
NK015(ba)006:14: gcig rnams sgra tshig rang mtshan las 'das phyir //
NK015(ba)006:15: dgongs brda'i brgyud par grags pa'i tshogs rnams la //
NK015(ba)006:16: gnas lug rang ngo 'phrod par gsol ba 'debs //
NK015(ba)006:17: gang tshe rigs gsum sems dpas rjes bzung ba'i //
NK015(ba)006:18: lha klu gnod sbyin srin po'i rig pa 'dzin //
NK015(ba)006:19: spyi dang bye brag gsang sngags 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK015(ba)006:20: ma la ya zhes gnam lcags yod pa'i rtser //
NK015(ba)006:21: gsang bdag dpa' bo'i rjes bzung byin rlabs pa //
NK015(ba)006:22: lha yi rig 'dzin grag ldan mchog skyongs dang //
NK015(ba)006:23: srin po blo gros thabs ldan klu 'jog po //
NK015(ba)006:24: gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong dang mi'i rig 'dzin //
NK015(ba)006:25: dri med grags pa nyid de rigs can lnga //
NK015(ba)006:26: gsang bdag rje dang li tsa bi gang gi //
NK015(ba)006:27: rjes bzung don dang tshig gi brgyud pa rnams //
NK015(ba)006:28: yongs 'dzin chos rgyal lung bstan rdo rje la //
NK015(ba)006:29: rgyud gsum don kun rtogs par gsol ba 'debs //
NK015(ba)006:30: rgyal po dzahzhesa grags pa gang de yis //
NK015(ba)006:31: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i smin grol gdams ngag gis //
NK015(ba)006:32: rjes bzung ku ku ra dza tshom bu 'bum //
NK015(ba)006:33: de bzhin in+t+ra bo ng+hi tshom bu khri //
NK015(ba)006:34: seng ha r+aa dza tshom bu stong dang ni //
NK015(ba)006:35: u pa r+aa dza tshom bu lnga brgya dang //
NK015(ba)006:36: sras mo go ma tshom bu brgya dang bcas //
NK015(ba)006:37: rig 'dzin sa la rim bzhin mngon gshegs pa'i //
NK015(ba)006:38: rig pa khyad par can gyi brgyud pa la //
NK015(ba)006:39: bsgrub 'bras tshe 'dir thob par gsol ba 'debs //
NK015(ba)006:40: de lta'i gdams zab go ma sa la yis //
NK015(ba)006:41: khyi rgyal phyi ma slob dpon sgeg rdor dang //
NK015(ba)006:42: bud+ha gu h+ya gsum la gnang ba las //
NK015(ba)006:43: ku ku r+aa dzas ro langs bde ba dang //
NK015(ba)006:44: drang srong b+ha shi ta gnyis la bshad de //
NK015(ba)006:45: lnga mas rdo rje bzhad pa la yang gnang //
NK015(ba)006:46: de dang b+ha shi ta yis za hor gyi //
NK015(ba)006:47: rgyal po pra b+ha ha sti la bshad nas //
NK015(ba)006:48: gang des o rgyan sangs rgyas gnyis par gdams //
NK015(ba)006:49: de bzhin sgeg ba'i rdo rje sangs rgyas gsang //
NK015(ba)006:50: rnam pa gnyis las b+ai ma mi ta yis //
NK015(ba)006:51: gsan nas rma gnyags zung gis bsgyur ba dang //
NK015(ba)006:52: sangs rgyas gsang ba nyid las bee ro rjes //
NK015(ba)006:53: gsan pa dang bcas brgyud pa'i srol gsum po //
NK015(ba)006:54: kun 'dzin babs so dang po gnyags yin phyir //
NK015(ba)006:55: dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra bcas mgon rnams la //
NK015(ba)006:56: sa lam gong du 'phel bar gsol ba 'debs //
NK015(ba)006:57: gnyags chen ye shes gzhon nu'i rjes bzungs pa //
NK015(ba)006:58: sog po dpal gyi ye shes gang de yis //
NK015(ba)006:59: gnub chen la bshad de bzhin rma gnyags kyi //
NK015(ba)006:60: thun mong slob ma khu btsun byang chub 'od //
NK015(ba)006:61: khyung po dbyig 'od gnyis las sda mas ni //
NK015(ba)006:62: zhang btsun rgyal ba'i yon tan la bshad cing //
NK015(ba)006:63: khyung pos dar rje dpal gyi grags pa la //
NK015(ba)006:64: bshad cing de las yongs grags dbus lugs dang //
NK015(ba)006:65: khams lugs zhes grags bka' srol gnyis pa gyes //
NK015(ba)006:66: zhang gis bshad pa gtsang bzung mchims phu mar //
NK015(ba)006:67: grags pa nyid de 'dir yang gnubs kyi gsan //
NK015(ba)006:68: gzhan yang rma nas mkhas pa gtsug gyer gnyis //
NK015(ba)006:69: brgyud pa sgyu 'phrul nar bu'i lugs sam ni //
NK015(ba)006:70: gdams lugs zhes grags de yang gnubs la babs //
NK015(ba)006:71: de phyir babs so gnyis pa gnub chen po //
NK015(ba)006:72: sangs rgyas ye shes zhabs la thugs sras bzhi //
NK015(ba)006:73: sras kyi dam pa gcig bcas lngar grags pa'i //
NK015(ba)006:74: nang tshan so btsun ye shes dbang phyug nas //
NK015(ba)006:75: rim bzhin dpa' thung byang chub rgyal mtshan dang //
NK015(ba)006:76: gong btsun shes rab ye shes gang de yis //
NK015(ba)006:77: gtsang gi ra thung shes rab tshul khrims la //
NK015(ba)006:78: de nas shes rab mchog dang nyang ye 'byung //
NK015(ba)006:79: yang na bu d+ha dz+ny+aa na'i thugs sras mchog /
NK015(ba)006:80: gnubs chung khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho nas //
NK015(ba)006:81: de sras ye shes rgya mtsho la brgyud de //
NK015(ba)006:82: nyang btsun shes rab mchog dang nyang chen po //
NK015(ba)006:83: ye shes 'byung gnas la brgyud srol gnyis ka /
NK015(ba)006:84: gsang bdag zur chen sh+aakya 'byung gnas la //
NK015(ba)006:85: gtod phyir babs so gsum pa gang de nas //
NK015(ba)006:86: zur chung shes rab grags dang de yi sras //
NK015(ba)006:87: ka chen bzhi dang gsang bdag sgro phug pa //
NK015(ba)006:88: sh+aakya seng ge nas brgyud sgyu 'phrul ni //
NK015(ba)006:89: bshad ka'i lugs zhes grags pa'i srol 'dzin pa'i //
NK015(ba)006:90: mkhas grub bla ma ji snyed byon rnams la //
NK015(ba)006:91: snang ba lha skur 'char bar gsol ba 'debs //
NK015(ba)006:92: khyad par sgyu 'phrul gdams ngag lugs zhes pa //
NK015(ba)006:93: gnyags kyi gsang chos slab bshad thun min rgyun //
NK015(ba)006:94: rma nas gtsug ru rin chen gzhon nu ngang //
NK015(ba)006:95: gye re mchog skyong gnyis la rim brgyud nas //
NK015(ba)006:96: dar rje dpal grags de yis gnubs chen la //
NK015(ba)006:97: bshad cing de nas rim bzhin spa gor gyi //
NK015(ba)006:98: blon chen 'phags pa dang ni tan yon tan mchog /
NK015(ba)006:99: gsal ba'i byang chub blo gros rgya gzhon nu dang //
NK015(ba)006:100: tshul mgar khrims bzang po ye shes mtshur dbang po'i zhabs //
NK015(ba)006:101: chos dag kyi dbang phyug mchog zhang gi bla ma dang //
NK015(ba)006:102: yon gyi tan 'byung gnas slob dpon gzhon don grub //
NK015(ba)006:103: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po klong chen pa //
NK015(ba)006:104: brtse chen thugs rje'i bdag nyid mgon rnams la //
NK015(ba)006:105: don dam chos sku rtogs par gsol ba 'debs //
NK015(ba)006:106: kun mkhyeen bla mas rjes bzung mkhas grub mchog /
NK015(ba)006:107: khyab brdal lhun grub nas brgyud rim pa bzhin //
NK015(ba)006:108: sprul sku grags pa 'od zer mkhas grub mchog /
NK015(ba)006:109: sangs rgyas dbon po chos rje zla grags dang /
NK015(ba)006:111: / 'bri gung kun bzang rdo rje rin chen phun tshogs zhabs //
NK015(ba)006:112: rong grol nyi zla sangs rgyas tshe dbang mkhan ma ni dang //
NK015(ba)006:113: snang mdzad rdo rje 'brug sgra bzang po'i sde /
NK015(ba)006:115: / 'phrin las lhun grub gter chen 'gro ba'i mgon /
NK015(ba)006:117: / 'gyur med rdo rje dang ni gang de'i gcung //
NK015(ba)006:118: mkhan chen d+harma sh+r+ai nas brgyud de //
NK015(ba)006:119: khri chen rin rnams de yis grub dbang mchog /
NK015(ba)006:120: sh+r+ai na tha la brtsal rje gang des //
NK015(ba)006:121: kun mkhyen phyi ma mkhyen brtse'i 'od zer la //
NK015(ba)006:122: gnang phyir snyan brgyud bla ma'i tshogs rnams la //
NK015(ba)006:123: bden gnyis dbyer med rtogs par gsol ba 'debs //
NK015(ba)006:124: mgon po gang des smin grol gdam pa'i mdzod //
NK015(ba)006:125: ma lus rang skal nyid du brtsal ba dang //
NK015(ba)006:126: chab gcig bdag gir bgyis nas bstan 'gro'i srog /
NK015(ba)006:127: gso mdzad kun gzigs byang chub rdo rje dang //
NK015(ba)006:128: skyabs mgon mchog des mdo sngags bstan pa'i khur //
NK015(ba)006:129: khyod gcig kho nas 'dzin la ma zhums zhes //
NK015(ba)006:130: bstan rtsar dbang bskur mdzad pa'i rig pa 'dzin //
NK015(ba)006:131: gzhon nu 'jigs med chos kyi blo gros sogs //
NK015(ba)006:132: mdor na rgyud rgyal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba yi //
NK015(ba)006:133: man ngag la brten grub gnyis mngon byas pa'i //
NK015(ba)006:134: rig 'dzin bla ma dam pa'i tshogs rnams la //
NK015(ba)006:135: blo 'das lta ba rtogs par gsol ba 'debs //
NK015(ba)006:136: de ltar dgongs brda' snyan khung rim brgyud pa'i //
NK015(ba)006:137: dam pa kun gyi gdams ngag gsang ba'i mdzad //
NK015(ba)006:138: ma lus bzung nas 'gro la rtsol mdzad pa'i //
NK015(ba)006:139: bka' drin 'khor med rtsa ba'i bla ma la //
NK015(ba)006:140: bskyed rdzogs mtha' ru phyin par gsol ba 'debs //
NK015(ba)006:141: gang zhig gsol ba btab pa'i re 'bras kun //
NK015(ba)006:142: thogs med yid bzhin 'grub pa'i byin rlabs dang //
NK015(ba)006:143: bdag sogs 'di nas tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK015(ba)006:144: mgon po rnams kyis rjes su 'dzin par shog /
NK015(ba)006:145: skyabs gnas bslu med dkon mchog rnam gsum dang //
NK015(ba)006:146: ma nor lam ston bla ma'i thugs rje yis //
NK015(ba)006:147: bdag gis yid smon gsol ba gang btab pa //
NK015(ba)006:148: de dag 'gro ba'i don du 'grub gyur cig /
NK015(ba)006:149: ces pa'ang mkhyen dpyod kyi blo gros mchog tu yangs
NK015(ba)006:150: pa'i sgrubs brtson zla ba grags pas gsung gis bskur
NK015(ba)006:151: ngor // deng dus kyi rgyud pa rnams kyis bla
NK015(ba)006:152: ma brgyud pa'i rim pa bde blag nyid du rtogs
NK015(ba)006:153: par bya ba'i phyir 'phros don cung zad kyis ngag
NK015(ba)006:154: sgo yangs par byas nas brjod pa po /
NK015(ba)006:155: mdo sngags bstan pa'i nyin byed grub dbang rdzogs chen
NK015(ba)006:156: pa yab sras kyi bka' 'bang gi gral mthar sdod
NK015(ba)006:157: pa po rgyal sras gzhan phan mtha' yas 'od zer
